What kind of person would you like to be?

----Royal------------------------------
In the land that you live, there are three very distinct groups of people.
Among these are the Royals. They have power and fame, but some families hold very dark secrets.




----------Pirate-----------------------
Beyond the palace walls, the sea ports bring pirates. The lives of the pirates hold adventure, but also danger.




--------------Assassin-----------------
Somewhere unseen, there are the assassins. 
They remain invisible and tend not to reveal their careers to the public. 
However, their lives are put in danger with each mission that is take.